values: HEY EVERYONE I WAS GOINGTO COME HOME FOR LABORDAY WEEKEND BUT PLANS HAVE BEEN CHANGED AND MY SHIP IS BEING SENT TO THE GOLF FOR ABOUT A MONTH TO HELP WITH RELIEF SUPPORT FOR TH HURRICANE DAMAGE. TALK TO EVERYONE WHEN I GET BACK

ok it has been really busy since i was home in december. i went to the middle east on the USS HARRY S. TRUMAN (CVN-75). i was out there from january 15th to april 18th. then we were on palm and worked 1 every 4 days for a month(that was great) then we started going out for short curises and that is still going on, in face we will be out again soon. as for job wise i want to MR "A" SCHOOL in chacigo from augest till dec of 04 and about 2 weeks now i am working in the locksmith shop learning about safes and how to work on locks and all that great stuff. i love it and should be going to locksmith school in kentucky, one of only a few civilian schools that actually transfer to the civilian world.so in 2 more years that is what i am going to be doing while going to college back in ny where i am origanlly from. living in va right now. lost touch of most of my friends however i am tring to track everyone down and see them while i go home. it isn't working but in 2 years it should be a lot easier. well that is a quick 5 min update i have to go and get things ready so i can go back to work again tonight. if u get a chance e-mail me. everyone how has ever had my e-mail it is still the same from highschool so call other people who knew me in highschool and write if u get a chance. talk to yall soon. stay safe and hope to hear fron yall soon

scuba-steve

wow it is amazing how when u are mad about something you can just get on the journal and write even if you never get on and write. for example tonight. today was ok and it was a good day untill about 9:30pm. between haveing plans and making last minute plans for the 15 mins i had before i was supposed to be else where it was last minute and i was givin a guilt trip about leaving the persons house who i was at for about 15 min and had to leave even though i was there for almost 30 min instead while holding up other poeples plans plans and then getting the cold shoulder yet again. i am tired of ny and its "you are too good of a friend" to date and the well i prefer you friend who is here instead. i miss chicago where i had friends who were intrested in me. knew when someone who was a good person and were friends with them instead of the people who didn't do anything. it is weird been around the would and friends online are thanking me for defending the country and people at home who don't know me and them friends tend to be to busy for me. i know i seem the same way but i have limited time in the area i whish i was able to stay and see everyone. i just want to move to chicago. i miss ashly, jessika, jessica, will and ali. they had fun and we all had a good time. i almost want to move to chicago when i am out of the navy. i have a great skill being set up so i will have a job almost anywhere but people in chicago exp. the girls actually liked to hang out with me and were intrested in ME!!! of while i will get there some other day. just glad to be home safe. a slight buzz at a top speed of 105 mph on back roads and 85 to 90 on the S bends was not the best idea exp when i was racoons crossing the roads. tomorrow i go back to va and i will have to see when i come to ny again. i am planning on going to chicago and visit jessika and her mom and ashly again. i miss the hospitality they gave a total stranger. maybe i will go there instead of my next time. well i miss yall and i will talk to you all soon. phone texting jessika at 2:51 am. talk to yall soon.

signed "SINGLE STEVE"

hey everyone how are yall. i know i am not on much that is because i am on another 6 month deployment. i can't way when i will be back from it but wanted to say hello because it is hard to call with a 9 hour time diffrence. how everyone is doing good and i will talk to you all again soon. keep in touch if you can. later.

Hey everyone hope yall are doing good. haven't talk to everyone as much as i would have liked to. haven't seen many of ya in a while and i was just home for about 3 weeks. I am back by VA. Beach again. the weather was like 60 for the past 3 days and just got cold again today. there is not to much going on, i wish i had drove back home again for new years eve. i had fun down here but i still wish i was home with one of my friends.don't think they read this but if so they know who there are. when i get to go back home again i will try to visit those who i have not been in contact with in a while. i still have to visit brian and terri again i only say them once while i was home. But i will talk to yall soon. things are going ok down here and i will talk to yall soon.

Steve

Ok before i get into other issues, tonight was a overall good night. left home about 6:00pm and went to visit ams at work but she wasn't there and i didn't get to talk when she got there, she had to work, then me and shawn went x-mas shopping and actually got something done. then i went to the bar with my parents and had a couple of drinks and then went bowling. plad three games while still drinking and then got home about midnight. only 3 drinks all night and 2 of which were free. and then talk to my stepfather about letting someone move in for a while if needed. not sure how that is going to go, i have to talk to him about it more later. well i want to make one of my good friends happy, i would do almost anything in the world for her. i would not mess up my whole world for her but i will do what i can to help her. right now looking for a car and tring to get it so she has a place to stay if needed. On the the next topic. lately i have been getting more and more depressed. i think i am falling for someone i have had a crush on since the 10th grade and yet i know it will never happen. but i want it to so much oh well i am leaveing and it is not worth haveing a relation ship while i am about 650 to 750 miles away. i just don't know what to do. well that and i am getting depressed about the fact that i am about to leave ny again soon. i have been here for almost 20 days and i have seen brian terri and ashly once, seen a lot of shawn and amber and treasea and seen my cousin shae only once. not seeing everyone i want to and i talk to my friends from chicago, aaron online, ashly only 4 times and jessika the night i got home. i wish i calk to to jessica B. and jessika more. i talk to jessika's cousin more then her which is kinda uncool oh well i guess she has moved on and forgot about me well not sure what else to write, right about now. got home and drinking more, parents were complaining that they bought me a 6 pack and only drank about 1/4 of one of the bottles since i got home on the 6th of dec and it's now the 22 of dec. no i am not a big drinker even though i have drank about 7-9 drinks at the bars, that is still not alot, 4 at panarama, 1 and pulse,3 at rose garden and 1 at the mug, 4 of those drinks were free to me, 2 for being in the navy one for being where i was and one for being my mothers son. well i am going to go and hope that things will workout for me. and i will talk to yall later

Signed
Sexy Steve.

last nights writing, I know it's been a while since my last update but i have been keeping very busy. Monday i meet a great girl(E) while at the mall(for the 3rd day in a row). that thursday me her and her friend(J) meet and played pool.. that next night me her(E) (J)(AR)(AS)(P) all went to a dance club about and hour south of where i am. got back and in bed about 3 :30am and work up about 7:45 am to get ready for the renisance faire. we all dressed up in chainmail and walked around till about 4pm then left and went and rested to get back up a few hours later to go bowling with (E), and (AR). dropped off (AR) and she brought me back to where i had meet them and parked my car and talked from about 1am to about 3:30am. very worth it. then about5:30 am went to bed to get about about 8:15 to go to (E) grandparents for a family party. (AR) also went with us.. We played a little ping pong for about an hour then went swimming for about 4-6 hours and played some water games for about 1-2 of those hours. while in the pool her little cousin asked her a question and i didn't really hear it but i heard her say "I don't know your have to ask him." so she swam to me and asked me if i was her boyfriend. didn't say yes or no just "i have only known her for about 3 days. after swimming played pool for about 30 and hung out till about 9pm. drove (AR) home and we talked and drove around for a little bit and she asked what i would have said if it was not for the family being around. well i told her i would have said yes and we drove around in circles for about and hour and a half brought her home around midnight and talked on the walkway for about 30 min before i left. not from about midnight on sunday. Monday we were supposed to go and play softball however when i got out of class she told me she could not talk and her car broke down in the middle of an intersection. so i wanted to go help her out but she said she was fine and had i ride and she would call back later. so i went out and played pool for about an hour and about 7:15 called her and her and she didn't answere her phone. said tuesday that she saw a movie monday night and was out till one and was going out with friends. i was having a horible day since monday morning and had duty tuesday so i would not be able to go and hang out with her. so tuesday night i wrote the top paragraph around 11pm because i was stuck up and was thinking about her all day. then today i was woke up really earily after bing up till about 1am in the morning for watch and forgot something and teacher sounded like he was going to be a dick. he turned out to be really cool though so i can't complain about him. was basicly told that i will not be allowed to take the MR# test because i got screwed over again like in march. so was madder and missed pt which is good because i was talking to the chief about the test. then had to clean till 5pm and finally got off about 5:30 pm went out. called (E) to she what she was doing now that we were going out and she said she could not talk at first then i played pool till about 9pm and about 10 pm i called her again and some guy answered and said that he had not her that name. seeing at it was her cell i called again and people just fucking with me on the phone. saying she was tied up litterly and say didn't seem like she wanted to tal and after she said they let her go i hear her asking for her pants back. just what i wanted to here thinking she was going to call me when she was going to go out. then i had some guy call about 3 min after she was getting ready to leave the other people saying that he was her boyfriend and she didn't want me to call her anymore after she just said that was not the case. so i told him if she said that i would believe it so he let me talk to her and she said that she was dating him since monday after we started going out at 10:30 pm sunday night. not even 24 hours and she said that he was not there while she was tied up and what not. so i don't know what to believe but it seem like when ever i actually like like someone to the point i want to be around them that they find the worst way to say they don't give a shit about me and didn't want to hurt me. so have your friends say they just fucked you 6 times and them a min later have you new boyfriend call me and to stop harassing you is the best way to let me know u don't really want to date. whatever. so pissed off i got back and went rollerblading on base. got pulled over by the cops just about the time i was not so pissed off anymore at about midnight and it's not 1 am and i am still pissed off about her and the fucking cop saying i can't roller blade. right now i just want to crawl in a hole and die. and on top of all the shit tonight i tried to call my friend before the whole episode with (E) to see how ams was doing. she went in for segury on the 17th to have a plate put in her head where her skull was missing from the crash and i got no answere and the answereing machine was diffrent so i want to know how she was doing. so i think i will be buld from stress by tomorrow morning. well i am going to go tos and turn while i TRY to sleep. and am stuck woundering about ams and thinking about how i really like (E). for the friends who want to see pics of me and the group of 9 who went to the renissance faire let me know and i will e-mail you a copy of the pics. talk to yall later, ther is if i don't have a anurism from stress and shit. night @ 1am
~SLEEVE~
